millimeters to a centimeter.

00:38:19.650 --> 00:38:21.950
If I went out into the
hallway and only pointed

00:38:21.950 --> 00:38:24.210
at the ceiling, the
area would go up.

00:38:24.210 --> 00:38:28.160
But as you walk around and build
more observations of the room,

00:38:28.160 --> 00:38:30.320
it can become more
precise over time.

00:38:30.320 --> 00:38:31.280
AUDIENCE: OK.

00:38:31.280 --> 00:38:31.780
